empt to grasp vast---even cosmic---realities.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 05. Dez 2022) 0aLiteraturexHistory and criticism. 0aMiniature objects in literature. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Historical.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478023548?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478023548423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478023548/original  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles